'''猶他奧克爾山聖殿'''（Oquirrh Mountain Utah Temple）是[[耶穌基督後期聖徒教會|耶穌基督後期聖徒教會]]的一座聖殿，位於[[猶他州|猶他州]][[鹽湖城|鹽湖城]]郊區的[[南喬丹_(猶他州)|南約旦]]。此城是世界上第一個有兩座聖殿的城市（此城也有猶他約旦河聖殿）。猶他奧克爾山聖殿是[[鹽湖谷地|鹽湖谷地]]的第四座聖殿，也是猶他州的第13座聖殿<ref>{{citation |contribution= Open House and Dedication Dates Announced for Oquirrh Mountain Utah Temple |url= http://www.mormonnewsroom.org/ldsnewsroom/eng/news-releases-stories/open-house-and-dedication-dates-announced-for-oquirrh-mountain-utah-temple |title= News Story |work= Newsroom |publisher= [[LDS_Church|LDS Church]] |date= January 31, 2009 |accessdate= 2012-10-15 |archive-date= 2019-02-16 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190216102447/https://www.mormonnewsroom.org/ldsnewsroom/eng/news-releases-stories/open-house-and-dedication-dates-announced-for-oquirrh-mountain-utah-temple |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

猶他奧克爾山聖殿為居住在鹽湖谷地的約83,000名後期聖徒服務。該建築面對著在中國採掘和碾磨的淺米色花崗岩。

''聖殿歷史''

猶他奧克爾山聖殿建在破曉社區邊緣的山崗上；<ref>{{cite web |first=Gordon B. |last=Hinckley |author-link=Gordon B. Hinckley |url=https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/ensign/2005/11/opening-remarks?lang=eng |title=Opening Remarks |date=November 2005 |journal=[[Ensign_(LDS_magazine)|Ensign]] |access-date=October 15, 2012 |archive-date=2020-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808182804/https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/ensign/2005/11/opening-remarks?lang=eng |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="#1">{{cite web |url=https://newsroom.churchofjesuschrist.org/article/new-salt-lake-valley-temple-announced |title=New Salt Lake Valley Temple Announced |work=Newsroom |publisher=[[LDS_Church|LDS Church]] |date=October 1, 2005 |access-date=August 18, 2019 |archive-date=2019-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629110434/https://newsroom.churchofjesuschrist.org/article/new-salt-lake-valley-temple-announced |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="#1"/>該遺址由肯納科特土地（Kennecott Land）捐贈給耶穌基督後期聖徒教會，肯納科特土地是一家開採奧克爾山銅礦和貴重礦物的公司的一部分，在聖殿西邊幾公里處。聖殿有一個高193英尺（59 公尺）的石尖塔，上面是一個9英尺（2.7 公尺）的天使摩羅乃雕像。 2006年12月16日，進行奠基儀式。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.deseretnews.com/article/650215784/Ground-broken-for-LDS-temple.html |title=Ground broken for LDS temple |first=Carrie A. |last=Moore |date=December 17, 2006 |newspaper=[[Deseret_News|Deseret News]] |access-date=October 15, 2012 |archive-date=2019-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190715185921/https://www.deseretnews.com/article/650215784/Ground-broken-for-LDS-temple.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>在奠基活動中，該聖殿被命名為“猶他奧克爾山聖殿”；它以前被稱為“猶他南約旦聖殿”。<ref name="Oquirrh Mountain Utah Temple information">{{cite news |title=Oquirrh Mountain Utah Temple information |url=https://www.thechurchnews.com/archive/2009-08-29/oquirrh-mountain-utah-temple-information-34238 |newspaper=[[Church_News|Church News]] |date=August 29, 2009 |access-date=October 15, 2012}}</ref>耶穌基督後期聖徒教會總會會長戈登·興格萊（Gordon B. Hinckley）主待奠基儀式。

這座聖殿坐落在遺址11英畝（45,000平方公尺）的土地，坐落在形成[[鹽湖谷地|鹽湖谷地]]西緣的奧克爾山腳下，向東朝著[[瓦薩奇山脈|瓦薩奇山脈]]的全景。遊客可以從聖殿遺址看到山谷中的其他三座運行聖殿：[[猶他德雷珀聖殿|德雷珀聖殿]]，[[猶他喬丹河聖殿|約旦河聖殿]]和[[鹽湖城聖殿|鹽湖城聖殿]]。

2009年6月13日，雷雨期間，尖頂被閃電擊中。天使摩羅乃的雕像被損壞，並於2009年8月11日被更換。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.deseretnews.com/article/705322723/Moroni-statue-replaced-at-Oquirrh-Mountain-Temple.html |title=Moroni statue replaced at Oquirrh Mountain Temple |first=Scott |last=Taylor |date=August 11, 2009 |newspaper=Deseret News |access-date=August 18, 2019 |archive-date=2017-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170910151247/http://www.deseretnews.com/article/705322723/Moroni-statue-replaced-at-Oquirrh-Mountain-Temple.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ksl.com/?nid=148&sid=7501114 |title=New Moroni statue placed atop Oquirrh Mountain Temple |date=August 11, 2009 |publisher=[[KSL-TV|KSL]].com |access-date=October 15, 2012 |archive-date=2017-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170910174945/https://www.ksl.com/?nid=148&sid=7501114 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在2009年8月21日至23日進行奉獻儀式之前，公眾應邀在2009年6月1日至2009年8月1日的開放日內參觀新聖殿。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://newsroom.churchofjesuschrist.org/ldsnewsroom/eng/news-releases-stories/open-house-and-dedication-dates-announced-for-oquirrh-mountain-utah-temple |title=Open House and Dedication Dates Announced for Oquirrh Mountain Utah Temple |work=Newsroom |publisher=[[LDS_Church|LDS Church]] |date=January 31, 2009 |access-date=August 18, 2019 |archive-date=2019-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190626120827/https://newsroom.churchofjesuschrist.org/ldsnewsroom/eng/news-releases-stories/open-house-and-dedication-dates-announced-for-oquirrh-mountain-utah-temple |dead-url=no }}</ref>
耶穌基督後期聖徒教會總會會長多馬·孟森（Thomas S. Monson）在他第82生日主待奉獻儀式。

2020年，因冠狀病毒大流行而關門了猶他奧克爾山聖殿。<ref>Stack, Peggy Fletcher. [https://www.sltrib.com/religion/2020/03/26/all-latter-day-saint/ "All Latter-day Saint temples to close due to coronavirus"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.sltrib.com/religion/2020/03/26/all-latter-day-saint/ |date=20200818145648 }}, ''[[The_Salt_Lake_Tribune|The Salt Lake Tribune]]'', 26 March 2020. Retrieved on 28 March 2020.</ref>

